###################
# Avoid SSH Prompt
###################

# https://devops.stackexchange.com/questions/725/can-i-bypass-host-key-checking-in-ansible
# http://docs.ansible.com/ansible/intro_getting_started.html#host-key-checking

This is typically done by setting the following value in ansible.cfg:

[defaults]
host_key_checking = False
If you don't want to modify ansible.cfg you can set an environment variable like so:

export ANSIBLE_HOST_KEY_CHECKING=False


